---
description: Global UI/UX and responsive standards
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow `docs/DESIGN.md` for every UI change.

Mandatory UI rules:
- Use Black/Blue/White palette with super-light-blue accents (no new purple accents).
- Build responsive UI for mobile, tablet, laptop, and desktop.
- For data tables, provide proper mobile restructuring (cards/stacked rows), not overflow-only.
- Think like a product designer for card hierarchy and scanability.
- Theme setup must use global CSS variables in `global.css` for both light and dark modes.
- Avoid hardcoded hex values when theme tokens exist.

